ty\n|Webster City\n|West Valley City\n|White City\n|Wolfe City\n|Yazoo City\n|Y City\n|Yuba City\n|Zama City\n|Zamboanga City\n|Zip City\n}}\n\n{{lookfrom|en|city}}\n\n====Related terms====\n{{col4|en\n|civic\n|civil\n}}\n\n====Descendants====\n* {{desc|dv|ސިޓީ|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|fi|city|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|fr|City|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|de|City|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ia|citate|der=1}}\n* {{desc|it|city|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ja|シティ|tr=shiti|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|sv|city|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|ru|си́ти|bor=1}}\n\n====Translations====\n{{trans-top|large settlement}}\n* Abkhaz: {{t|ab|ақалақь}}\n* Afrikaans: {{t+|af|stad}}\n* Ahom: {{t|aho|𑜋𑜦𑜧}}\n* Akkadian: {{t|akk|𒌷|tr=âlu}}\n* Albanian: {{t+|sq|qytet}}\n* Altai:\n*: Southern Altai: {{t|alt|кала}}, {{t|alt|тура}}\n* Ambonese Malay: {{t|abs|kota}}\n* Amharic: {{t+|am|ከተማ}}\n* Arabic: {{t+|ar|مَدِينَة|f}}, {{t+|ar|بَلَد|m}}\n*: Egyptian Arabic: {{t|arz|بَلَد|tr=balad}}\n*: Gulf Arabic: {{t|afb|مَدينَة|f|tr=mədina}}\n*: Juba Arabic: {{t|pga|mediina}}\n*: Moroccan Arabic: {{t|ary|مدِينَة|tr=mdīna}}\n* Aragonese: {{t|an|ziudá|f}}\n* Aramaic:\n*: Hebrew script: {{t|arc|מְדִינְתָּא|f|tr=məḏīntā}}, {{t|arc|כַּרְכָּא|m|tr=karkā}}\n*: Syriac: {{t|arc|ܡܕܼܝܼܢܬܿܵܐ|f|tr=məḏīttā}}, {{t|arc|ܟܿܲܪܟܿܵܐ|m|tr=karkā}}\n* Argobba: {{t|agj|ኸተም|tr=xatame}}\n* Armenian: {{t+|hy|քաղաք}}\n* Aromanian: {{t+|rup|cãsãbã|f}}\n* Assamese: {{t|as|নগৰ}}, {{t|as|চহৰ}}\n* Asturian: {{t+|ast|ciudá|f}}\n* Avar: {{t|av|шагьар}}\n* Azerbaijani: {{t+|az|şəhər}}\n* Bashkir: {{t|ba|ҡала}}\n* Basque: {{t+|eu|hiri}}\n* Belarusian: {{t|be|го́рад|m}}, {{t|be|ме́ста|n}}\n* Bengali: {{t+|bn|শহর}}, {{t+|bn|নগর}}\n* Betawi: {{t|bew|kota}}\n* Bhojpuri: {{t|bho|शहर}}\n* Breton: {{t|br|keoded|f}}, {{t|br|keodedoù|p}}, {{t+|br|kêr|f}}, {{t+|br|kêrioù|p}}\n* Bulgarian: {{t+|bg|град|m}}\n* Burmese: {{t+|my|မြို့}}\n* Buryat: {{t|bua|хото}}\n* Carpathian Rusyn: {{t|rue|мі́сто|n}}\n* Catalan: {{t+|ca|ciutat|f}}\n* Cebuano: {{t|ceb|dakbayan}}, {{t|ceb|siyudad}}\n* Chagatai: {{t|chg|آباد}}\n* Chamicuro: